Package com.github.cyberryan1.netunoapi.events.punish

Class NetunoPrePunishEvent

java.lang.Object
com.github.cyberryan1.netunoapi.events.punish.NetunoPrePunishEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
NetunoCancellableEvent, NetunoEvent
public class NetunoPrePunishEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements NetunoEvent, NetunoCancellableEvent
This event is fired before a player is punished. Note that for IP punishments, this event is only fired for the main punishment, not any of the reference punishments.
